  "instructions": [
    "Heat canola oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and carrot, sauté until onion translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in sliced mushrooms and turmeric, cook another 3 minutes.",
    "Gently add cubed tofu and nuka-pickle, tossing to coat, cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and lemon juice, bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add chopped spinach and simmer for 5 minutes until spinach wilts.",
    "Season with salt, adjust to taste, and remove from heat.",
    "Serve hot, optionally garnished with fresh herbs or a squeeze of lemon."
